Sentence: Furthermore, PGE ( 2), an EP2 agonist ( butaprost), an EP2 / PGE ( 3) ( EP3) / EP4 agonist ( misoprostol), and misoprostol in the presence of AH6809 all induced IL - 6 production, whereas an EP1 / EP3 agonist ( sulprostone) did not.
